{"tid":1490164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿警方逮捕學生 印尼示威者火燒議會大樓","createTime":"2019-08-20T04:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T03:19:55.000Z","uid":212626,"like":93,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"96756c9ecaf8af7984eb5ff761fcbf87cbd6e1d5","tid":1490164,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:46:19.000Z","msg":"印尼管轄的西巴布亞省今天爆發騷亂，數千名示威者縱火燒當地議會大樓，抗議印尼警方17日衝進大學宿舍，逮捕涉嫌毀損印尼國旗的43名滋事學生。<br />\n<br />\n人在現場的法新社記者估計，數千示威民眾湧入西巴布亞（West Papua）省首府曼諾瓦里（Manokwari）街道，以致這座約有13萬人口的城市陷入癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n部分抗議人士縱火燒毀商店和車輛，搗毀交通號誌，並朝著政府大樓丟擲石塊。<br />\n<br />\n西巴布亞省副省長拉科塔尼（Mohamad Lakotani）告訴羅盤電視台（Kompas TV）：「<span style=\"color: red;\">議會大樓遭縱火，市中心、市場、港口和商店都遭波及，全部的活動基本上都陷入癱瘓。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，示威者扔擲石塊傷及3名員警，目前尚不清楚是否有任何示威民眾受傷。當局今天下令當地學校停課。<br />\n<br />\n這場騷亂起因於大學生被逮捕的新聞報導。報導說，警方17日突襲印尼第2大城泗水（Surabaya）的一所大學，發射催淚瓦斯逮捕43名學生。8月17日是印尼獨立74週年紀念日。<br />\n<br />\n當地媒體和巴布亞異議人士表示，身穿鎮暴裝的警察衝進一間宿舍，發射催淚瓦斯，以逮捕被控毀損印尼國旗的學生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3998066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F3998066&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuUBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=b885437c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3998066</a>"},{"pid":"e265712fa34c54cc6b2d885e44e0ea108e009384","tid":1490164,"uid":79793,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QRmdNqk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQRmdNqk.jpg&h=3ab6c83d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3351a12c16130f54ff383585e6222fed8fb1348f","tid":1490164,"uid":10079,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:47:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無分和勇 上下一心<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"d76fcd1c6286ee3e1d1213c10e48233eb4cda7a0","tid":1490164,"uid":242323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:47:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"348cfe7ad4d2b29da6d9a456418c74f3a6eb7fe8","tid":1490164,"uid":43668,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"阻唔到香港人返工其實做咩都得"},{"pid":"a27ba74ce980536eb5b3406ecb7c6b4448d9d69e","tid":1490164,"uid":212626,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"香港人真係已經好温和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印尼一有人被捕<br />\n就直接火燒重要建築物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857c7f12e9d81f38d8479ced3bb2989ad8d97fa0","tid":1490164,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b679765f319fcb55133c80ab070e9b0bd1f8e93","tid":1490164,"uid":108337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"好好學習"},{"pid":"e439e13cb9be322763bbf3db1df791170b149e97","tid":1490164,"uid":70227,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:51:23.000Z","msg":"香港人暴動個意思：飛磚同鐵枝<br />\n但唔會周圍打爆野<br />\n燒車放火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e193f1e1f1b361319c6e6921201cd96fb5f3fe2e","tid":1490164,"uid":16034,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無計啦印尼本身就生番國家 邊有港豬咁多包袱可言<br />\n下次捉到黑警/藍絲打人根本就要私刑 咁撚有道德係無用架"},{"pid":"678e511ca871be89bfb7d87482f203aa22bd1892","tid":1490164,"uid":289946,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥<br />\n🔥🔥🔥🏢🔥🔥🔥<br />\n🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥<br />\n😱😱</span>"},{"pid":"cbb1cd9b5aa5a26797d545a8347678540bb79f98","tid":1490164,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e439e13cb9be322763bbf3db1df791170b149e97","tid":1490164,"uid":70227,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"c